To confirm the accuracy of the MDIF SIME routine, errors due to estimating the WB microparameters (Eq. (4)) with the SIME routine were evaluated. The MDIF was generated as described above and used to fit the six VOI TACs (Table 1) to the irreversible 2TCM solution (Eq. (3)) in the standalone fitting routine. Then, the best-fit estimates of the four parameters (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
