				\begin{document}$$\rho$$\end{document}ρ = 0.96, p < 0.001). Similarly, average (± standard error) regression for WM had a slope of 0.82 ± 0.06 [0.69 to 0.95] and an intercept of 1.7 ± 0.7 µmol/100 g/min [0.2 to 3.1 µmol/100 g/min] (R2 = 0.92, \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
